        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer838635819" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16134267818588803904">For me this book was great. Being a army mom I struggle seeing my son being deployed and in the military. I have seen or heard many people who deal with ptsd. survivor guilt and many struggles that soldiers have. But saying that he shows how people can fall in love and find love where they dont expect it. A promise to someone can lead to so much more. The joys of small towns and all the ins and out of that and also jealousy that people have and the lengths that people would do. This is a great b</span>
  <span id="freeText16134267818588803904" style="display:none">For me this book was great. Being a army mom I struggle seeing my son being deployed and in the military. I have seen or heard many people who deal with ptsd. survivor guilt and many struggles that soldiers have. But saying that he shows how people can fall in love and find love where they dont expect it. A promise to someone can lead to so much more. The joys of small towns and all the ins and out of that and also jealousy that people have and the lengths that people would do. This is a great book to read. I would recommend it </span>
